  "Background Story": {
    "Upbringing": "Norrie Is was born at the heart of the Misty Forest, a verdant haven sheltered from the turmoil of the outside world. Raised by a community of wandering bards and scholars, Norrie's early years were steeped in the rich lore and diverse music of the Forgotten Realms. As an Elf, Norrie possessed a natural affinity for magic and art, talents that flourished under the tutelage of the community's elders. Despite the peaceful surroundings, Norrie was always driven by a restless curiosity, yearning to explore beyond the forest's ethereal mists.",
