    "Motivations and Adventure Hook": "Driven by a desire to protect the Realms and its myriad cultures, Norrie now seeks to unravel the mystery of the prophecy, fearing the consequences of its fulfillment. With their background as a Bard and Faction Agent, Norrie is uniquely equipped to gather allies, decipher the cryptic verses, and thwart the looming threat. Yet, questions remain: What is the nature of the evil mentioned in the prophecy? And can it truly be stopped, or is the Forgotten Realms doomed to face a darkness it cannot overcome? This quest for answers promises to be Norrie's greatest adventure yet, pulling them into the depths of ancient mysteries and perhaps revealing secrets about their own heritage along the way."
  }
